data.description: Welcome to this beautifully updated 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home with an exquisite inground pool! Nestled in a peaceful neighborhood, this charming residence offers a perfect blend of modern features.  Upon entering, you'll immediately notice the open-concept layout, providing a sense of spaciousness and seamless flow between the living areas.  The updated kitchen with stainless steel appliances, ample storage space, and a convenient area that can be used for a desk or made into a coffee bar.   Other notable features of this updated home include energy-efficient windows, and a two-car garage providing ample parking, RV parking, refrigerated central ac, and large backyard!   Call today to setup a viewing of this home before it is gone!
